videoDetails.title: DJ Premier - Top 10 Beats
videoDetails.shortDescription:
Here at BeatGrade we decided to do our own Top Ten series of great producers. This feature is the Legendary and Great DJ Premier. He has produced for some of the Best MC's and albums of all time. 

He has produced beats for his group Gang Starr, Nas, KRS One, WU - Tang Clan, The Notorious B.I.G., Common, Jay- Z, and more.  This selection of beats we chose are not only some of our favorites, but the most influential beats we feel DJ Premier has produced. This was also not based on what were his Big successes. Premier also just had a legendary beat battle with RZA from the Wu playing some of these classic beats. The list was hard to choose, but here's our Top 10 Beats from DJ Premier.

***If there's a producer who's beats you feel we should list, please say their names in the comments below!
